# Expense Insurance Claims Gross Amount

## identifier
de8481

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of insurance claims expense recognised during the relevant period, gross of any associated insurance recoveries. This item is to be determined in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

This item is calculated as the sum of paid claims and the movement in outstanding claims liabilities over the relevant period.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Insurance.ClaimsGross.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.05
- period=duration
